  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>One thing aldeka and I talked about on IRC is adding a tab called "Attend
events!" that is this calendar widget.

We also agreed that the "outreach events" phrase in the mission, at the top of
the page, should link somewhere related to events. Three reasonable places come
to mind:

1) openhatch.org/wiki/Events
2) events.openhatch.org
3) linking to the events tab within the page

Of these, I prefer option 3.

Pushing this to 0.11.10 because it's the end of September, but I am happy to put
this toward the top of my queue.</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
  <tr>
   <th><a href="msg2528">msg2528 (view)</a></th>
