  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>To avoid time zone difficulties, the front page's description of events should
probably say "In about 4 hours" and "In about 1 week" rather than "on Saturday,
11:30 PM".</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
  <tr>
